段將焦點轉移<br />\n目的係令勇武同警方對立<br />\n從而令成件事失焦<br />\n而且。事實上兩個月以黎我地底牌見盡<br />\n勇武唔係唔work但我地宜家既訴求係五大，<br />\n而非港獨。若然長久下去定必步雨傘後塵。<br />\n警隊正正係因為理得你宜家先失民心<br />\n但佢地well paid for it<br />\n我地尼？以武制暴並非高明。失去手足600人。一個訴求都得唔到，<br />\n長久下去市民就會認為我地搞事，我地一失民心就玩撚完。以武制暴係可以用。但要適當武力。<br />\n再者，警方只係政治棋子，無必要同佢對立。<br />\n對立同仇警對五大毫無幫助。<br />\n<br />\n我認為下一步要做既<br />\n就係政府點還手我地就點打<br />\n佢話我地鼓吹港獨，我地就唔用光複香港時代革命<br />\n佢話我地不合作運動阻住人返工既權利<br />\n我地就暫時唔搞不合作運動<br />\n直接搞全城再罷工，或癱瘓經濟。<br />\n<br />\n另外係時候準備文宣<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>無限放大五大訴求，警察濫權及警黑勾結</strong></span><br />\n將所有人眾返埋一齊。<br />\n<br />\nBtw <br />\n絕對支持真。光復香港，時代革命<br />\n但仲未係時候。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:06:41.000Z","msg":"無限放大警黑勾結<br />\nThis is the main point: after the attack on 21 July, a lot of government supporters has become neutral (rather than supporting the government). They know who is behind the people in white. Even the government supporters fear the people in white. So we should not use violent for a while to avoid scaring the general public. All we should do is to this propaganda: <br />\n<strong>無限放大警黑勾結. The people in white destroys the safety of Hong Kong.</strong>"},{"pid":"811884ceaed1c981b1c5a4ba691fa68636179ba2","tid":1427213,"uid":278524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:08:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f967a36c34f549d7140b5ca8b1aa813ee528e161","tid":1427213,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f765b526c78084ef97c067e12abf3959c42c58fb","tid":1427213,"uid":9138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:01:11.000Z","msg":"咁啫係畀政府牽住鼻走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:11:17.000Z","msg":"We will win because after the elections at the end of this year, the parties that support the government will lose a lot of seats.<br />\n<br />\nAt  this moment, do not let the government has a chance to fight back. The government has waited for a long time before the fight back since 6/8/2019. We can also waited and win the election later."},{"pid":"7bfcb7d15fd3e6ee161980d70e2847a3b463d6bd","tid":1427213,"uid":144636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:25:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"caa333d9c5089bcfe744edecec7dd74cdeefd558","tid":1427213,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:28:25.000Z","msg":"一係收隊9月玩大專戰<br />\n<br />\n迫d黑警仔女斷社交  全校都乞憎<br />\n<br />\n黑警最愛仔女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n9月義士要讀好d書  <br />\n<br />\n長期抗爭  讀書都好重要<br />\n<br />\n唔專心讀比d 5毛狗霸晒大學都好大獲"},{"pid":"0a8d1a0e3319976009a05ce017ce21f777fcd1dc","tid":1427213,"uid":144636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:00:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"748b2deaf69cf68330f23a1b71eb9d50d537215b","tid":1427213,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:01:45.000Z","msg":"甘？"},{"pid":"229f2316b58dddbe31f5e1fb54e64a9e7f44a0d8","tid":1427213,"uid":129506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:09:45.000Z","msg":"甘你老母"}]}